# Flutter Apps (User & Driver) Rules

- **Files:** snake_case (e.g. `sos_confirmation_screen.dart`).
- **Classes:** PascalCase (e.g. `SosConfirmationScreen`).
- **Structure:** Feature-first — `features/<feature>/presentation/`. Shared in `core/`, `shared/`.
- **Widgets:** Use `const` constructors. Extract when reused or > 50 lines.
- **State:** One approach (Provider/Riverpod/Bloc). Keep logic out of UI.
- **API:** Typed models, handle errors, show SnackBar/Dialog.
- **Platform:** Use `Platform.isAndroid` or conditional imports. Test on emulator + device.
